1
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:34,860
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,250 --> 00:01:37,600
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,400
It's raining so heavily.

4
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:49,759
Let's go home.

5
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,229
My wife and kids
are waiting for me at home.

6
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:53,950
Let's go home.

7
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:59,990
[Mingguang Grand Theater]

8
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,160
Where on earth did you go?

9
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:12,800
Murong Qingyi,

10
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:17,280
what kind of life did you live before?

11
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:29,000
You are a member of the Murong family.

12
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:32,200
You don't have to be ordered around
by others all the time.

13
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,590
What if I don't apologize?

14
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:35,430
Are you going to kill me today?

15
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:36,680
How many times
have you targeted your sister-in-law?

16
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,520
Everyone else is innocent.

17
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,590
I'm the only bad seed,

18
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:41,050
the disgrace of the Murong family,
alright?

19
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,000
Susu,

20
00:02:51,670 --> 00:02:54,280
no one in this world understands you
better than I do.

21
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,470
I'll say it again.

22
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,600
Don't meddle in my business.

23
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,470
Since it's destined,

24
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,710
why should we struggle?

25
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:12,630
Wontons!

26
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,100
Have a bowl of wontons!

27
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:24,840
Is it good?

28
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,460
At a time like this,

29
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,710
a bowl of hot soy milk would be great.

30
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:33,320
But soy milk is only sold in the morning.

31
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:35,310
I'll take you to Nancheng someday.

32
00:03:35,310 --> 00:03:38,030
There's a late-night snack stall there
where you can buy soy milk.

33
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:40,360
My mom used to take me there
when I was a kid.

34
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,430
Do you take your mom there now?

35
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,310
Here comes the soy milk.

36
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,710
Drink slowly. It's hot.

37
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,310
Qingyi.

38
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:25,690
[Zeng Yinqiu, Li Rongzhang's Wife]

39
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,000
I seem to have forgotten.

40
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:36,290
You don't know how to use it yet, do you?

41
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,600
I can just drink it from the bowl.

42
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,760
Why are you here?

43
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:20,080
Li Rongzhang just came
and made a big scene,

44
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:23,560
saying that the Huo family had severed
the tendons in your hand in prison.

45
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,920
He demanded the Murong family

46
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:27,780
compensate him
with 200 boxes of rifle ammunition.

47
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:29,120
That old fox.

48
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,240
He never lets himself lose out.

49
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,600
Why didn't you tell Qingyu?

50
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,120
He forced me to confess

51
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,320
and sent me to prison.

52
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:42,880
Would he believe it?

53
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:47,250
Back then, the Huo family was pushing hard

54
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,600
and insisting on killing you.

55
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,000
To save your life, Qingyu

56
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,760
used all his connections

57
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:56,310
and had no choice
but to send you to prison for 3 years.

58
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:57,830
I just think it's ridiculous that you

59
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:58,830
couldn't clear up

60
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,100
such a simple misunderstanding.

61
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,680
Did you come all the way here

62
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,950
just to make me mad?

63
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,560
You told me before

64
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,220
that when you're in a bad mood,

65
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,100
you come to this shop for soy milk.

66
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,360
So?

67
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:29,680
Right at this moment,

68
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,950
you have to cling to me.

69
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,770
Seeing me look like a loser,

70
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,830
are you very happy?

71
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:36,490
I never thought of it that way.

72
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,560
I'm also responsible...

73
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,540
for what happened.

74
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:48,600
I know.

75
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,800
You just want Qingyu to misunderstand.

76
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:55,159
You want him to think
that I am targeting you.

77
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:55,920
This way,

78
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,830
no matter what I say in the future,

79
00:06:57,830 --> 00:06:58,960
he won't believe it.

80
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,270
Right?

81
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:01,800
About the wedding dress,

82
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,800
I was just trying to protect myself.

83
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:09,490
But I'm talking about Huo Mingxi.

84
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,120
If I hadn't killed him...

85
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,050
-your hand...
-No need to explain.

86
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:17,920
I know.

87
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,100
You were just doing what you had to do.

88
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:23,800
And I

89
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:26,070
just happened to be

90
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:27,670
the one you didn't consider.

91
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,770
It was like this in the past,

92
00:07:32,510 --> 00:07:34,110
and it's still like this now.

93
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,190
Your brother now

94
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:46,480
hates the Huo family to the core.

95
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,810
Isn't that a good thing?

96
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:49,510
You want to deal with the Huo family.

97
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,800
This way, my brother

98
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,370
can become your weapon.

99
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:55,110
You're really going to marry
the right person.

100
00:07:57,310 --> 00:08:00,040
I got some information
out of Li Rongzhang today.

101
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,190
The Huo family's vault

102
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,790
probably has a huge problem.

103
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,920
The Huo family
does charity on the surface,

104
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,920
but behind the scenes,
it's all dirty business.

105
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,750
They collect orphans from everywhere,

106
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,720
divide them into different classes,

107
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,980
sell them as laborers,

108
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,750
sell their organs,

109
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:16,400
or deliberately maim them so they can beg.

110
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,800
Those with good looks

111
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:21,070
will be sent to a mysterious auction

112
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,050
to be sold to the rich and powerful.

113
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,240
This is the latest list

114
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,190
of missing girls from the orphanage.

115
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:28,920
Perhaps

116
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:30,480
you want to join me

117
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:33,210
to seek revenge against the Huo family
yourself.

118
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:34,840
What do you mean?

119
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,760
Whether you want to use me

120
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,600
or just pity me,

121
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,610
I don't want to play along.

122
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,000
And also,

123
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,640
you shouldn't

124
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:49,400
come to this place anymore.

125
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,010
It's not very suitable...

126
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:53,380
for the young miss of the Fang family.

127
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:02,480
Maybe it's right for him to do this.

128
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:05,070
Staying away from me,

129
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:07,750
just as I always wanted.

130
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:11,230
[Benevolence as the Foundation,
Healing to Save the World]

131
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,390
If I had never appeared,

132
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,390
you could have had a better life.

133
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:39,660
♪ Hate is the smoke left by dying flames ♪

134
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:43,150
♪ Love is the warmth
lingering after the wildfire ♪

135
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:42,550
Thank you, Doctor.

136
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:46,910
♪ Love and hate collide in a blaze ♪

137
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:44,750
Don't mention it.

138
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:45,200
Don't forget your medicine.

139
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:45,800
Thank you.

140
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:50,680
♪ Devour me all ♪

141
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:54,020
♪ Ahead lies
a tangle of joys and sorrows ♪

142
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:57,860
♪ Behind remain
the bitterness of unspoken feelings ♪

143
00:09:58,010 --> 00:10:01,530
♪ The heart races with every thought ♪

144
00:10:01,570 --> 00:10:04,730
♪ As long as we loved each other,
I don't care ♪

145
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:08,490
♪ Is it a blessing or a curse? ♪

146
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,080
Susu,

147
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:13,790
♪ If the sparks ♪

148
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,240
do you believe me?

149
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:13,600
I will definitely

150
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,200
become the best surgeon.

151
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:16,700
♪ Could fly back into the gun's muzzle ♪

152
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:23,790
♪ If I had turned away
when love first bloomed ♪

153
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:32,090
♪ Perhaps I could've
walked away unscathed ♪

154
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:38,500
♪ Sadly, fate leaves no room for "if" ♪

155
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:54,720
[Murong Residence]

156
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:07,400
Where have you been?

157
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,640
Even if I die outside,

158
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,730
what does it have to do with you?

159
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,090
You're an adult now!

160
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,320
Disappearing whenever you want!

161
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,030
Running away from home!

162
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,390
Do you know there are people
who are worried about you?

163
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,030
Who?

164
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:30,360
Cheng Jinzhi?

165
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,550
Or Murong Jinrui?

166
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:32,320
Or Li Rongzhang?

167
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,030
Me!

168
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,460
I looked for you all night!

169
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:38,750
Fine.

170
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,920
Then beat me to death.

171
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:43,400
Come with me!

172
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,080
I'm sorry.

173
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:09,540
This gentleman was severely injured

174
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:10,510
back then.

175
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,870
Although he has recovered now,

176
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:15,000
he should still experience occasional

177
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:17,480
dull pain and spasms.

178
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:20,480
Can't his hand fully recover?

179
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:22,000
My brother is a surgeon.

180
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:23,560
His hand cannot be damaged.

181
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:24,840
His hand

182
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,390
can handle

183
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:27,750
daily life,

184
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,840
but to recover

185
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:32,110
to the precision required for surgery,

186
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:33,630
I'm afraid

187
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,240
there's nothing I can do.

188
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:36,840
Is there no other way?

189
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:38,960
I'm sorry.

190
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,670
I told you it's pointless.

191
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:41,270
It can't be restored.

192
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:42,870
You insisted on coming here.

193
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,370
Such a waste of time.

194
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,080
Stop right there!

195
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,480
I told you to stop!

196
00:12:55,510 --> 00:12:56,360
If this hospital doesn't work,

197
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,620
we can try another one.

198
00:12:57,870 --> 00:13:00,390
I heard there's a good hospital
in Hangcheng.

199
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,120
We can try again there.

200
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,720
Stop being so hypocritical.

201
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,150
I don't need you
to seek medical help for me.

202
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:06,480
It's just a ruined hand.

203
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:08,730
It just means I can't be a surgeon.

204
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:11,200
I can still be the scapegoat
for the Murong family.

205
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:13,510
I can still be a stepping stone for you.

206
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,100
It's not enough, is it?

207
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,320
If it's not enough,

208
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,910
you can ruin my right hand too.

209
00:13:18,910 --> 00:13:19,770
Is that enough?

210
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,790
Serve Young Master Qingyi well.

211
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:36,870
He's locked up here.

212
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:38,960
It seems the Murong family

213
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,240
doesn't care about his life

214
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,480
as an abandoned pawn.

215
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,730
Murong Qingyu, remember this.

216
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:06,960
You were the one who sent me to prison.

217
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:10,410
Why are you acting
like a good brother now?

218
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:12,480
You are no different

219
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,270
from Cheng Jinzhi

220
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,840
and Li Rongzhang!

221
00:14:20,390 --> 00:14:21,670
I'm sorry!

222
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:30,720
It was my fault.

223
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:37,720
It was my fault.

224
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:42,350
I remember back then,

225
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,200
when you finally recovered,

226
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:48,870
I asked you

227
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,150
what you wanted to study.

228
00:14:53,270 --> 00:14:55,000
You told me without hesitation

229
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:57,840
that you wanted to study medicine.

230
00:14:58,510 --> 00:14:59,510
So I

231
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:02,120
sent you to study abroad

232
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:04,890
so you could study medicine well.

233
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:08,380
You occasionally wrote to me.

234
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:10,690
The contents of those letters

235
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,960
were all about medical knowledge.

236
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,440
Actually, at that time,

237
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,000
I was happy for you.

238
00:15:26,870 --> 00:15:28,330
I was really happy for you.

239
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,260
You finally came back to this family.

240
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,860
You didn't trust anyone else.

241
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:54,960
You could only trust me.

242
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:14,000
Enough.

243
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,970
Stop being so sentimental.

244
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:25,000
Actually,

245
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,620
it doesn't hurt that much now.

246
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:34,870
Now,

247
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:38,440
what can I do for you

248
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,270
to make you feel better?

249
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:44,450
I will definitely satisfy you.

250
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,600
There really is one thing

251
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,480
you can do for me.

252
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,560
Let me take another bite.

253
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:12,790
-This illness is so scary when it flares up.
-Get out!

254
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:14,069
He is so young.

255
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,720
-Young Master Qingyi...
-Qingyi, don't be afraid.

256
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:16,720
I'm your brother!

257
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:20,550
Hang in there!

258
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,000
You can do this!

259
00:18:25,930 --> 00:18:29,220
[Huo Residence]

260
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,040
Young Master,

261
00:18:35,270 --> 00:18:37,070
a letter from the Murong family.

262
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:40,890
[Letter of Annulment]

263
00:18:41,310 --> 00:18:42,510
Letter of annulment?

264
00:18:43,270 --> 00:18:44,160
Who sent it?

265
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:46,160
That bastard Murong Qingyi?

266
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,360
It was Murong Qingyu.

267
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:50,640
We've already had the engagement ceremony.

268
00:18:50,170 --> 00:18:53,500
[I hereby announce that the engagement between
my younger brother and Miss Minxian is dissolved.]

269
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:53,400
He can't just cancel the engagement
whenever he wants.

270
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,480
Murong Qingyu also asked me
to pass on a message.

271
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,240
Tell me.

272
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:57,720
What is it?

273
00:18:59,590 --> 00:19:00,450
What did he say?

274
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:03,280
"The losses of the Huo family

275
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:05,920
are not enough to cover even a fraction
of my brother's medical bills.

276
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:07,090
If the Huo family can't accept it,

277
00:19:07,090 --> 00:19:07,760
[I hereby announce that the engagement between
my younger brother and Miss Minxian is dissolved.]

278
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:10,660
you can come to the Cheng Army
and ask me for compensation."

279
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:21,530
[Linglong Cheongsam]

280
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:26,270
[Closed]

281
00:19:26,380 --> 00:19:27,930
[Nancheng Main Sewer System Map]

282
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,510
A few days ago,

283
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:29,900
I secretly investigated the Huo family.

284
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:33,160
[Huo family] [Zhenhua Aviation School]
[Church] [Xanadu Cabaret] [Dongjiadu]

285
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:33,440
This is the route map
for their goods transportation.

286
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:35,000
I found female hair

287
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,590
in one of the supply carts,

288
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:38,720
as well as the lingering smell
of sulfur soap.

289
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:39,750
I remember the orphanage

290
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,440
has always used this kind of soap.

291
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,350
So,

292
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:43,640
these supply carts

293
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:46,120
were indeed used to transport these girls.

294
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:48,270
But why transport them to Dongjiadu?

295
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:48,930
[The Latest Map of Nancheng]

296
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:52,680
Perhaps delivering supplies for charity
to Dongjiadu

297
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:54,610
is a way for them to cover things up.

298
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,680
But what method did they use

299
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,920
to transfer the girls to another place

300
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,160
after bringing them to Dongjiadu?

301
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:01,150
[Church] [Xanadu Cabaret] [Dongjiadu]

302
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:02,750
[Huo family] [Zhenhua Aviation School]
[Mingguang Grand Theater]

303
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:03,570
If they are trafficking these girls,

304
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:04,940
they must have a venue.

305
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:06,790
The most reasonable explanation is that

306
00:20:06,790 --> 00:20:08,070
Dongjiadu can directly lead to

307
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:09,200
that trading venue.

308
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:13,440
Where is the Huo family's Hong Fang Bank?

309
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:16,000
You suspect Hong Fang Bank
is the shipping location?

310
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,200
How is that possible?

311
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:18,480
Dongjiadu is a slum,

312
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:21,270
while Hong Fang Bank
is in the most prosperous wealthy area.

313
00:20:21,270 --> 00:20:23,400
Besides, Hong Fang Bank
is the foundation of the Huo family,

314
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:23,780
[Dongjiadu]

315
00:20:23,550 --> 00:20:25,000
having operated legally for decades.

316
00:20:23,780 --> 00:20:26,410
[Hong Fang Bank]

317
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:27,880
Would the Huo family really carry out

318
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,240
such a dirty business there?

319
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,440
Both sides of Dongjiadu

320
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:33,020
[Church] [Dongjiadu]

321
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:32,430
are ordinary residential areas.

322
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:34,480
One side has
the church and charity hospital.

323
00:20:33,060 --> 00:20:35,670
[Church] [Charity Hospital]

324
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:35,790
The other side

325
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,200
is a ditch.

326
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:39,010
There is nothing unusual.

327
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,550
A ditch?

328
00:20:44,350 --> 00:20:45,150
What's wrong?

329
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:49,080
Besides the street map,

330
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,070
