of the sewer lines in this area?

331
00:20:49,430 --> 00:20:51,990
[Ditch]

332
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:53,420
[Church] [Xanadu Cabaret] [Dongjiadu]

333
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:54,590
[Huo family] [Zhenhua Aviation School]
[Mingguang Grand Theater]

334
00:20:55,270 --> 00:20:57,070
Dongjiadu and Andeya Road

335
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,770
are simply two different worlds.

336
00:20:58,770 --> 00:21:03,880
[Dongjiadu] [Ditch] [Hong Fang Bank]

337
00:20:58,830 --> 00:21:00,070
Who would have thought

338
00:21:00,070 --> 00:21:01,270
that they are only separated by

339
00:21:01,270 --> 00:21:03,350
this short ditch.

340
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,790
So the girls from the orphanage,

341
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:08,450
after arriving at Dongjiadu,

342
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,700
