343
00:21:11,350 --> 00:21:12,880
to Hong Fang Bank.

344
00:21:13,730 --> 00:21:15,190
[Hong Fang Bank]

345
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:28,590
I've already asked someone

346
00:21:28,590 --> 00:21:30,510
to find the best doctor in the country

347
00:21:30,510 --> 00:21:32,640
to come to Nancheng to treat your hand.

348
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,720
It's pointless.

349
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,110
Why is it pointless?

350
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:36,030
If it doesn't work here,

351
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:37,070
