352
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:38,240
You must get treated.

353
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:39,440
You can go if you want,

354
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:40,640
but I'm not going.

355
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:45,070
I haven't wanted
to be a surgeon for a long time.

356
00:21:45,070 --> 00:21:47,270
As for my hand, it's fine as it is.

357
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:48,590
Stop fussing.

358
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:53,010
Then what do you want to do?

359
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:57,480
I want to see someone

360
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:58,960
lose to me.

361
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:00,830
Who?

362
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:05,840
Just someone from the past.

363
00:22:07,550 --> 00:22:08,880
I lost to her before.

364
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:10,310
I can't accept it,

365
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:11,920
so I want to win.

366
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:18,160
Alright.

367
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,970
It's good that you have such an obsession.

368
00:22:22,310 --> 00:22:23,970
Then win it back beautifully.

369
00:22:24,790 --> 00:22:26,030
But some things

370
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:27,940
are actually not worth it.

371
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,560
Let it go when you should.

372
00:22:32,110 --> 00:22:33,790
Let it go when you should?

373
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:36,480
Then can you...

374
00:22:37,270 --> 00:22:39,330
just let things go whenever you want?

375
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:43,040
For example, you and that...

376
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,440
Ms. Ye.

377
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:46,000
Can you?

378
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,920
I was with Ye before.

379
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:54,770
-Then why did you say...
-But that's all.

380
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:57,060
My engagement to Mulan won't change.

381
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,530
That's all you need to know.

382
00:23:04,590 --> 00:23:06,550
Not marrying the woman you like

383
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:07,920
and marrying Fang Mulan instead?

384
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:09,850
I don't know what you are thinking.

385
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:15,240
I met Miss Fang in Nanyang.

386
00:23:16,310 --> 00:23:17,510
Her father is like...

387
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,240
