431
00:25:46,270 --> 00:25:46,920
Well...

432
00:25:47,820 --> 00:25:50,960
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

433
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:48,960
A beige shirt,

434
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,820
grey trousers,

435
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,370
and a silver brooch.

436
00:25:52,110 --> 00:25:53,310
Young Master Murong?

437
00:25:54,030 --> 00:25:55,440
Even the Principal is here?

438
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:57,510
How does the Principal
know so much about Ms. Ye?

439
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:58,070
Well...

440
00:25:58,070 --> 00:25:58,730
Principal,

441
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:02,030
our police station will definitely
do its best to investigate.

442
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:03,430
But don't worry too much.

443
00:26:03,550 --> 00:26:05,200
You must take care of yourself.

444
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,110
Ms. Ye

445
00:26:06,110 --> 00:26:07,200
is an adult.

446
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:09,790
Maybe she had an emergency
and went back to her hometown.

447
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:10,720
She is an orphan.

448
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:11,790
Her relatives in her hometown

449
00:26:11,790 --> 00:26:13,050
didn't treat her well.

450
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:15,190
I've never heard of them.

451
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:16,030
Besides,

452
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:18,300
she is a very responsible person.

453
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:19,640
She would never do that.

454
00:26:20,750 --> 00:26:22,880
The missing person is a teacher
from our aviation school.

455
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:24,240
Judging from the current situation,

456
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:26,510
something unexpected must have happened.

457
00:26:26,510 --> 00:26:27,350
So please,

458
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:28,750
do your best.

459
00:26:28,750 --> 00:26:30,550
We will definitely do everything we can

460
00:26:30,550 --> 00:26:31,400
to find Ms. Ye.

461
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:34,930
Let's go.

462
00:26:36,350 --> 00:26:37,550
Stop gathering around.

463
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:45,360
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

464
00:26:37,590 --> 00:26:38,520
Go back to class.

465
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:41,050
Principal. Principal.

466
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:43,070
I have dispatched our men to look for her.

467
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:45,400
Her neighbors said
Ms. Ye hadn't returned for a day

468
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:48,070
and that nothing unusual
had happened recently.

469
00:26:48,070 --> 00:26:50,270
We searched the place
where Ms. Ye volunteered as a teacher,

470
00:26:50,270 --> 00:26:51,530
but we didn't find her.

471
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:54,110
Keep searching.

472
00:26:54,110 --> 00:26:54,640
Yes.

473
00:26:54,980 --> 00:26:56,850
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

474
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,720
Principal, where are you going?

475
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:12,070
Qingyu.

476
00:27:13,270 --> 00:27:14,200
Are you sure this is the route

477
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,730
Ms. Ye must take to commute?

478
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:18,830
You observed the footprints

479
00:27:18,830 --> 00:27:20,110
and studied the soil.

480
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:22,640
And after all that,

481
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,920
Inspector Li, you still need to ask?

482
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:27,150
The traces are too messy now.

483
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:27,920
Indeed,

484
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:30,170
my skills still need improvement.

485
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:31,700
If your skills are poor...

486
00:27:31,830 --> 00:27:33,110
This is indeed the route Ms. Ye

487
00:27:33,110 --> 00:27:35,310
takes to the aviation school every day.

488
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:57,000
Silver Hademen.

489
00:27:58,030 --> 00:28:00,360
It seems there was indeed a struggle here.

490
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:15,720
-Go!
-Go!

491
00:28:15,790 --> 00:28:16,270
Go!

492
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:18,070
Who are you?

493
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:30,350
These bushes

494
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:32,320
show signs of a struggle.

495
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:45,680
Found it.

496
00:28:48,640 --> 00:28:49,400
This is it.

497
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:51,200
This is the brooch

498
00:28:51,350 --> 00:28:52,880
Ms. Ye was wearing that day.

499
00:28:56,070 --> 00:28:57,070
Hong Fang Bank?

500
00:28:57,590 --> 00:28:58,720
It's the Huo family.

501
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:01,400
The cigarette butt from earlier
didn't have a tax stamp.

502
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,480
It must have been smuggled out

503
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:03,610
by factory workers.

504
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:04,510
Give me some time.

505
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:05,400
I can find these people.

506
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,270
By the time you find them,

507
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:08,670
Ms. Ye won't even have
bone fragments left.

508
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:09,310
Qingyu,

509
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:11,070
Since we know it's the Huo family,

510
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:13,440
