and demand that they hand her over.

511
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,640
Search thoroughly.

512
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,230
It's best if the Huo family

513
00:29:16,230 --> 00:29:18,030
hasn't had time to transfer her.

514
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:20,030
-If we can't find her...
-If we can't find her,

515
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:21,490
I will make a bigger scene.

516
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,260
We need to let them know

517
00:29:25,350 --> 00:29:26,480
that those who dare
to lay a finger on my brother's woman

518
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,720
will pay the price.

519
00:29:32,470 --> 00:29:33,470
Causing trouble—

520
00:29:33,590 --> 00:29:34,390
I'm good at it.

521
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:44,160
Qingyu.

522
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:46,680
Do you need me to go back
and call more people?

523
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,920
With people from the police station there,

524
00:29:47,920 --> 00:29:49,980
the search will be more justifiable.

525
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:53,500
Don't get involved

526
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,510
in this for now.

527
00:29:57,100 --> 00:29:58,670
[Tung Teh Road]

528
00:29:58,700 --> 00:30:01,240
[Hong Fang Bank]

529
00:30:03,270 --> 00:30:03,790
Miss,

530
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:04,850
