531
00:30:14,380 --> 00:30:17,500
[Hong Fang Bank]

532
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:27,680
Hello, Madam.

533
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:30,070
What kind of business would
you like to handle?

534
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:31,070
Asset custody.

535
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,510
Then our Hong Fang Bank's custody services

536
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:37,830
