537
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:37,730
[Hong Fang Bank]

538
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:39,200
[Hong Fang Bank]

539
00:30:42,270 --> 00:30:43,720
I'm not interested in

540
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:45,870
