544
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:56,650
I will arrange for someone to introduce
our business to you in detail.

545
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,490
Madam, this way please.

546
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:06,920
Please.

547
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:08,750
Madam,

548
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,130
this way please.

549
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:24,270
May I have your last name?

550
00:31:24,270 --> 00:31:25,160
My last name is Wang.

551
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,920
I am a property consultant dedicated to

552
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:28,920
serving our distinguished guests.

553
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:31,170
Manager Wang, you're so thorough.

554
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,830
No wonder Hong Fang Bank

555
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:34,830
can stand alongside Huaxi and Chada

556
00:31:35,070 --> 00:31:37,030
in a place like Nancheng,

557
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:38,350
where the strong gather.

558
00:31:38,350 --> 00:31:39,210
You flatter us.

559
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:41,030
